:39:35.000Z","msg":"香港人、fight back<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a8687698dab37be4cde2ae2821a41541e03c5b","tid":1627203,"uid":184688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73324532e0d491c9c1277f8cd89124a8283ef59f","tid":1627203,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:51:26.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"1073bfdd511271041a3a84b42950f9e2a6b418c1","tid":1627203,"uid":184688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca92c86c79197827a277c3f39079f4ae44c632b1","tid":1627203,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b19709a8af4cddedf417e47292ead1d5b17ffa6f","tid":1627203,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb921e0ca98dd5fa5317c2abb809dab8d4a224c","tid":1627203,"uid":184688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc411f75aa7a81c09e179546f7918ff12980c5ff","tid":1627203,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"571feff0875b7913683975055d1cebee6ae94dc2","tid":1627203,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64aad575a885bf94601480387b5b22e304340bf2","tid":1627203,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6b365108e64ab400744fce24bceaef7215e339","tid":1627203,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4f59c7be9b76b07dacdf25f6a74d51eaae59671f","tid":1627203,"uid":327193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa370e6b9d680883c55ade29ba2aeb913a6564e7","tid":1627203,"uid":8125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"aa0bbe5f65ec3216ed7f2c550dec6b8f1f6a3f01","tid":1627203,"uid":323930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:51:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dca8cdac97ef0ca0bc3bc13cafd4d5b4a03635e3","tid":1627203,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀推"},{"pid":"4d79608c441f125c6cab1bbed15c6a7a4b792e75","tid":1627203,"uid":84433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"124758d00cdbbab30a696ddced0af9fc39ae3a34","tid":1627203,"uid":52748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5fc69ebb0bd384141baaa66